{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/migratingto1.16"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigrationGuides"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"code":".appStorage","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" strategy used with ","type":"text"},{"code":"@Shared","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" now uses key-value observing instead of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"NotificationCenter","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" when possible. Learn how this may affect your code.","type":"text"}],"kind":"article","sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There are no steps needed to migrate to 1.16 of the Composable Architecture, but there has been"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a change to the underlying behavior of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".appStorage"},{"type":"text","text":" that one should be aware of. When using"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".appStorage"},{"type":"text","text":" with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@Shared"},{"type":"text","text":", if your key does not contain the characters “.” or “@”, then changes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to that key in "},{"code":"UserDefaults","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be observed using key-value observing (KVO)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Otherwise, "},{"code":"NotificationCenter","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be used to observe changes."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"KVO is a far more efficient way of observing changes to ","type":"text"},{"code":"UserDefaults","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and it works cross-process,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as from widgets and app extensions. However, KVO does not work when the keys contain “.”","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or “@”, and so in those cases we must use the cruder tool of ","type":"text"},{"code":"NotificationCenter","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". That is not","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as efficient, and it forces us to perform a thread-hop when the notification is posted before","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"we can update the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@Shared"},{"type":"text","text":" value. For this reason it is not possible to animate changes that are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"made directly to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UserDefaults"},{"type":"text","text":":"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["withAnimation {","  \/\/ ⚠️ This will not animate any SwiftUI views using '@Shared(.appStorage(\"co.pointfree.count\"))'","  UserDefaults.standard.set(0, forKey: \"co.pointfree.count\")","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In general, we recommend using other delimeters for your keys, such as “\/”, “:”, “-”, etc.:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["@Shared(.appStorage(\"co:pointfree:count\")) var count = 0"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}]}],"metadata":{"role":"article","modules":[{"name":"ComposableArchitecture"}],"roleHeading":"Article","title":"Migrating to 1.16"},"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.19","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.18","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17.1","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.